{"tid":213912,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺連登仔好中意笑人有夢想","createTime":"2017-04-23T12:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T09:50:53.000Z","uid":26249,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1e42f3ecf85ab574db04b797894bb652d43c57","tid":213912,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"其實成個香港都係<br />\n我唔明點解有夢想係一件可恥可笑既事<br />\n你地冇夢想咪算 點解要踩低人地？<br />\n其實無論個夢想有幾低微都好 <br />\n就有佢既價值係到 個份價值對你黎講可能一文不值<br />\n但對佢黎講可能意義重大<br />\n自己生活得行屍走肉咁 冇夢想冇目標<br />\n就眼紅人地活得好過你？<br />\n你自己做唔到既野 點解要令其他人都做唔到？<br />\n自己飛唔到就要阻止人飛？<br />\n咩心態黎？<br />\n多得你地不斷踐踏人地既夢想<br />\n香港先有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝哂<br />\n有感而發 歡迎負皮<br />\n<br />\n係香港 做乜都要比人踩 尤其係連登"},{"pid":"def6656bfe76e01fdec01e6d3adffbfbd458486c","tid":213912,"uid":46504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"緊係啦 宜家上緊網呀 我笑鳩你又唔會小忽肉 又有得宣洩<br />\n何樂而不為<br />\n<br />\n利伸：有夢想"},{"pid":"88697d63471da5306987649bd81352033c8d3ba0","tid":213912,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"夢想就係比人恥笑先有實現既價值<br />\n如果比人笑比人踩就縮咁都係算把啦<br />\n利申：有夢想"},{"pid":"6d0916769e7c7181d89cb7eef6e42125a74b8889","tid":213912,"uid":30348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i67FQ8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi67FQ8F.jpg&h=a228beb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4dd66aec7fbdb083a5a16d58e6af01eea413554","tid":213912,"uid":30348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i67FQ8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi67FQ8F.jpg&h=a228beb2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申 有夢想"},{"pid":"ba1ec5e8b66f2219d0ca25ae0e520934d50c12ff","tid":213912,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"